body:
Hey everyone, today on Quintus i somehow managed to get an 81 block shot, and was heaps proud of myself, so here it is:

http://imgur.com/di5pqVW

But then i thought theres got to be some competition to this, so everyone:
If you have proof (a screenshot) of your longest bow kill in Nebula please post it and i might arrange a top ten list or something :)

BUT the only rule is that your photo can't be from a TDM, I'm only looking at DTM shots

Good luck and enjoy :)

1. MunnaEclipse (221.24)
2. DeNando (151.99)

6. pope_panda (110.15)
7. pope_panda (108.62)
8. alfoanazco (97.51)

10. pope_panda (75.43)
